<subSubSection id="23E8F2D0014F0BC983DA6BF82FC8B0BA" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="14FCE7F0488C4834A4FB173FAB89E5A2" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C4BED71FE3F48CCC265300C2F66E12EF" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<bibRefCitation id="F7A458ADEC5DA8A91F947011E4C0C6A1" author="Thach, NN" journalOrPublisher="The Festivus" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="240 - 242" refId="B43" refString="Thach, NN, 2015. Bertiasetzeri, a new species of land snail from Vietnam (Gastropoda: Stylommatophora: Dyakiidae). The Festivus 47: 240 - 242" title="Bertiasetzeri, a new species of land snail from Vietnam (Gastropoda: Stylommatophora: Dyakiidae)." volume="47" year="2015">Thach (2015)</bibRefCitation>
recognised four nominal species in 
<taxonomicName id="E66DB71B02B9DE95E8D505BBBA54A5EF" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Bertiaceae" genus="Bertia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Bertia" order="Coronophorales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="BD73126C0A2F719488F779713E4051CD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Bertia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
: &quot; 
<taxonomicName id="9147F0938AA436BE6E11009C6E7F1A04" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Bertiaceae" genus="Bertia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Bertia" order="Coronophorales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="BF0203C1F1C342A267F83596DF38B537" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Bertia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
&quot; 
<taxonomicName id="49ADB0A52B1BE106ECAD1242409DB4AB" lsidName="brookei" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="brookei">
<emphasis id="68F8AC3D6AFD0B22AE0F4A97566DE88B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">brookei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Adam &amp; Reeve, 1848), 
<taxonomicName id="F3BDC72CE06608CA2CF174BB874346E6" genus="B." lsidName="B. cambojiensis" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="cambojiensis">
<emphasis id="72B1C95F1319DE089C762DFD39554BC1" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B. cambojiensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(type species), 
<taxonomicName id="2476439D3491BF340A6FF955418FDBB9" genus="B." lsidName="B. pergrandis" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="pergrandis">
<emphasis id="B1C15E8E94CA086F2D3C7D4DFF7D7AFC" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B. pergrandis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Smith, 1893) and 
<taxonomicName id="A30EB4B842AA52D5D1EE3097305BDDCF" genus="B." lsidName="B. setzeri" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="species" species="setzeri">
<emphasis id="DEC6BDCBB7B6196A85B283E83C449204" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">B. setzeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Thach, 2015. Nevertheless, he had overlooked key characters of the genitalia published by 
<bibRefCitation id="90A9B0C285FA6442DCA8CA6D2CA89598" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1469-7998.1891.tb06805.x" author="Godwin-Austen, HH" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="22 - 47" refId="B14" refString="Godwin-Austen, HH, 1891. On a collection of land shells made in Borneo by Mr. Everett, with descriptions of supposed new species. Part II. Zonitidae and Helicinidae. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London 59: 22 - 47" title="On a collection of land shells made in Borneo by Mr. Everett, with descriptions of supposed new species. Part II. Zonitidae and Helicinidae." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1469-7998.1891.tb06805.x" volume="59" year="1891">Godwin-Austen (1891</bibRefCitation>
: pl. 6, fig. 6) and 
<bibRefCitation id="80956A750FA4F8F44CAB180A47426663" author="Schileyko, AA" journalOrPublisher="Annals and Magazine of Natural History, Series" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" refId="B37" refString="Schileyko, AA, 2003. Treatise on recent terrestrial pulmonated mollusks. Ariophantidae, Ostracolethaidae, Ryssotidae, Milacidae, Dyakiidae, Staffordiidae, Gastrodontidae, Zonitidae, Daudebardiidae, Parmacellidae. Ruthenica, Supplement 2, Part 10: 1309-1466." title="Treatise on recent terrestrial pulmonated mollusks. Ariophantidae, Ostracolethaidae, Ryssotidae, Milacidae, Dyakiidae, Staffordiidae, Gastrodontidae, Zonitidae, Daudebardiidae, Parmacellidae. Ruthenica, Supplement 2, Part 10: 1309 - 1466." year="2003">Schileyko (2003</bibRefCitation>
: 1345, 1346, fig. 1758). The Bornean endemic species, 
<taxonomicName id="9CFFA1A14DBE2F118359427989298CB3" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix brookei" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="brookei">
<emphasis id="6311A05C644B85D15711E3E1D583321B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Helix brookei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Adam &amp; Reeve, 1848, exhibits a long and cylindrical gametolytic sac, lacks an epiphallus and amatorial organ complex, and a caudal foss and a caudal horn is absent; characters that unequivocally distinguish this species from the 
<taxonomicName id="DD006BA469C0DB2358E20FF12C40D37B" family="Dyakiidae" lsidName="" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" rank="family">Dyakiidae</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="13401BBABBCCE87674225184939527EF" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1469-7998.1891.tb06805.x" author="Godwin-Austen, HH" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="22 - 47" refId="B14" refString="Godwin-Austen, HH, 1891. On a collection of land shells made in Borneo by Mr. Everett, with descriptions of supposed new species. Part II. Zonitidae and Helicinidae. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London 59: 22 - 47" title="On a collection of land shells made in Borneo by Mr. Everett, with descriptions of supposed new species. Part II. Zonitidae and Helicinidae." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1469-7998.1891.tb06805.x" volume="59" year="1891">Godwin-Austen 1891</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="A12622FDAF5CBD89EB72EF7447CA517C" author="Laidlaw, FF" journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Malacological Society of London" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="190 - 201" refId="B19" refString="Laidlaw, FF, 1931. On a new subfamily Dyakiinae of the Zonitidae. Proceedings of the Malacological Society of London 19: 190 - 201" title="On a new subfamily Dyakiinae of the Zonitidae." volume="19" year="1931">Laidlaw 1931</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="2AD1C7EF1EA320D3D2CA56FC42463A1E" author="Sutcharit, C" journalOrPublisher="The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="279 - 287" refId="B42" refString="Sutcharit, C, Tongkerd, P, Tan, AS-H, Panha, S, 2012. Taxonomic revision of Dyakiajanus from Peninsular Malaysia (Pulmonata: Dyakiidae), with notes on other sinistrally coiled helicarionids. The Raffles Bulletin of Zoology 60: 279 - 287" title="Taxonomic revision of Dyakiajanus from Peninsular Malaysia (Pulmonata: Dyakiidae), with notes on other sinistrally coiled helicarionids." volume="60" year="2012">Sutcharit et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
). It is clear that 
<taxonomicName id="2867D1983D6A6DB8628E1A683CDCEF2B" class="Gastropoda" family="Helicidae" genus="Helix" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Helix brookei" order="Stylommatophora" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="brookei">
<emphasis id="7DBCC2F2DA13B0C48C8D61E7A71BE8AB" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Helix brookei</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Adam &amp; Reeve, 1848 does not belong in 
<taxonomicName id="79BB2F828D812157DBEC41AD5A7D07DA" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Bertiaceae" genus="Bertia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Bertia" order="Coronophorales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5D8E42B754E54B854D2D30BA6DB4CB79" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Bertia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and we recognise the following three as 
<taxonomicName id="F671D17EF9E26D92AE3EF675F6FF2FA4" class="Sordariomycetes" family="Bertiaceae" genus="Bertia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Fungi" lsidName="Bertia" order="Coronophorales" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Ascomycota" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="6AFFE48AFDDAE4B4487CFA1458BA3C07" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Bertia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species.
</paragraph>
